org.activebpel.rt.axis
Interface IAeWsdlReference

All Superinterfaces:
IAeCatalogListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
AeWsdlReference
public interface IAeWsdlReference
extends IAeCatalogListener

Container class for wsdl properties that are accessed via AeMutableServiceDesc. Will update its properties if the underlying wsdl is replaced.
